Package: CoTRA
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Toolbox for RNA Sequencing Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Umair", "Seemab", email = "u.seemab@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a Shiny graphical interface for bulk RNA-seq and single-cell RNA-seq analysis. CoTRA integrates data upload, quality control, differential expression, enrichment, annotation, clustering, trajectory analysis, and report generation workflows.
